{"tid":2272064,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[撞車hi花請教] 轉彎泵把hi到人腰位","createTime":"2020-11-05T01:19:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T05:36:54.000Z","uid":40350,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"3f52f63bc75ec894bea62794f3a62cb77b3cb830","tid":2272064,"uid":40350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T01:19:49.000Z","msg":"事緣係咁，我係內線洗衣街準備轉左入亞皆老街，隔離有車轉緊中線，我就開始轉<br />\n示意圖：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sP37DZW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsP37DZW.jpg&h=871239b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左邊感覺到無曬位 （撞完朋友落車僅僅夠格硬落），右邊逼到好埋，所以我收左油，結果我泵把花曬hi到佢腰位一條痕<br />\n<br />\n我未撞過車，佢當下話唔好塞住後面，咁我就駛埋一邊，但撞完當下蠢左無影相，之後先影返，佢聲稱有車cam，我咁岩拆左落黎清data （我知我on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n最後佢覺得佢係轉返自己條線，我就覺得係佢騎左入黎，報左警等下一步<br />\n<br />\n呢種情況想知我有無理虧，我知自己點都蝕底左，想請教下大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k0kNDZd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk0kNDZd.png&h=15cdddb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4UkU3qR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4UkU3qR.png&h=adca507d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d91971213eb91c6aee6f9ac579bc01641bfabeca","tid":2272064,"uid":161732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T01:23:43.000Z","msg":"個下應該係睇對方左邊車身有無過線？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留名學野"},{"pid":"bd106da676be679c8ccdd911773f5d7dd5dce309","tid":2272064,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T01:23:52.000Z","msg":"覺得自己無錯就打死都唔認啦<br />\n以前無車cam咪又係咁 咪等黑警查<br />\n但郁車呢下真係弱智"},{"pid":"0752e2e54f2fde5ddf6f3eadf76559ba50058ab1","tid":2272064,"uid":127024,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T01:24:22.000Z","msg":"有車cam贏9成<br />\n你轉彎要睇人頭 贏埋你10成<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵保險傾下點賠"},{"pid":"1c055895b9a402cab0708f2577766f6cfa231fbd","tid":2272064,"uid":120955,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T01:26:52.000Z","msg":"郁左車無相無cam無得傾喎<br />\n跌錢當買教訓下次記得醒啲<br />\n依家態度好啲希望對家唔好劏你算啦"},{"pid":"7c4f5feffb06bd32c11cb0c09a06bd05a29d5a65","tid":2272064,"uid":127024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0752e2e54f2fde5ddf6f3eadf76559ba50058ab1","tid":2272064,"uid":127024,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T01:24:22.000Z","msg":"有車cam贏9成<br />\n你轉彎要睇人頭 贏埋你10成<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵保險傾下點賠"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T01:29:08.000Z","msg":"自膠 冇睇清楚兩架一齊轉<br />\n如果佢大車轉呢啲彎實壓到線<br />\n啲狗通常幫車cam個邊 下次小心啲"},{"pid":"8d7264631e6e6c45e82abf33027fb04695a738a0","tid":2272064,"uid":217301,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T01:30:09.000Z","msg":"你撞到人腰即係後車已經輸一半， 同埋轉左彎通常拋向外， 好少你講對方既情況食入內彎， 同埋佢有車cam 的話大概都睇到有無過線， 佢無明顯過線肯定你輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58abc490e862236cdac69b54487d27afa4b12460","tid":2272064,"uid":116696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T01:34:38.000Z","msg":"呢個位梗係唔會平排轉啦<br />\n一前一後或者中線轉彎個架應該遲小小先扭駄<br />\n防止撞到/被內線車撞到"},{"pid":"209f993e416a12c784d204f79896305dd590ea0f","tid":2272064,"uid":290416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T01:38:43.000Z","msg":"如果兩架車都郁緊，你撞人身車，應該係你輸<br />\n如果撞之前你停曬，佢郁車撞到你就仲有得講下<br />\n但又無車cam，撞完又郁左車，都輸9成？"},{"pid":"52704591fc9d2b0625327e9fe2bc295c758d4245","tid":2272064,"uid":40350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58abc490e862236cdac69b54487d27afa4b12460","tid":2272064,"uid":116696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T01:34:38.000Z","msg":"呢個位梗係唔會平排轉啦<br />\n一前一後或者中線轉彎個架應該遲小小先扭駄<br />\n防止撞到/被內線車撞到"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T01:41:46.000Z","msg":"我岩岩開始轉 佢轉到一半 其實大概突左個頭 我收左油讓佢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi